{
  "id": "RAW_89f1060a",
  "title": "今日开源（2025-11-25）：微软发布 Fara，7 亿参数多模态 SLM，开创本地计算机使用 Agent 技术新范式",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==&mid=2247500563&idx=1&sn=0645c094aa92a979dc98237152916b88",
  "date": "2025-11-25 10:03:00",
  "author": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "siteName": "机器之心SOTA模型",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：Fara</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"382\" data-imgfileid=\"100016896\" data-ratio=\"0.3277777777777778\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1166\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=22d2215d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxVmPWFFeEkavAlbnNGrPn9tQeibZ9uewFRxK3VhR2UJSxiaXrb2GBSRnGISKnviaf9kLz2D3rq651xg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Fara是微软推出的首个专为计算机使用设计的小型语言模型（SLM），具有7亿参数。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">作为一款</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">超紧凑的计算机使用Agent（CUA）</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，Fara-7B在其体积类别中实现了最先进的性能，并与更大、更耗资源的Agent系统竞争。该模型采用</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">多模态解码器架构</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，能够处理图像（截图）和文本上下文，直接预测带有具体参数的思维和行动。Fara-7B专注于在网页上执行高层次用户任务，如预订餐厅、申请工作、规划旅行和购物清单。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/fara\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/fara</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：H</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">ypnos-i1</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5435185185185185\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1166\" data-height=\"634\" data-imgfileid=\"100016901\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3ae42001&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxVmPWFFeEkavAlbnNGrPn9nscGwaVUKhXe4qicFfRWa3KPRvozaR9jHicdrfhe1EgQ77egSDeVrEUQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Hypnos-i1-8B 是一个基于 Nous Hermes 3 (Llama 3.1 8B) 的专用推理模型，旨在在复杂逻辑、连锁思维推理和数学问题解决方面表现出色。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目是混合</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">量子-经典机器学习</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">的独特实验。与标准微调不同，Hypnos i1 使用由 IBM Quantum Heron 处理器生成的真实熵数据进行训练，这种“量子噪声注入”作为随机正则化器，旨在提高模型的创造力并打破生成中的确定性模式。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/hypnos-i1\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/hypnos-i1</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️框架平台、必备工具</span></strong></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：google-ai-mode-scraper</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.26481481481481484\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" data-height=\"308\" data-imgfileid=\"100016898\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4206f8a3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxVmPWFFeEkavAlbnNGrPn9HmpIA9fGmxuvjAcbaXIVb91FN5HyzRpOKzyG59ezC5DL8MowEbcIWg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Google AI Mode Scraper 是一个基于 Web Scraper API 的工具，能够在大规模上可靠地抓取 Google AI Mode 的响应而不被阻止。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">它可以将解析后的数据以 JSON 格式返回，并自动处理Agent、无头浏览器和反机器人系统。该工具适用于支持 SEO 和 GEO 项目、构建训练数据集或其他数据任务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/google-ai-mode-scraper\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/google-ai-mode-scraper</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②项目：FedVLR</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"290\" data-imgfileid=\"100016899\" data-ratio=\"0.25\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1162\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b1530fd3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxVmPWFFeEkavAlbnNGrPn9WUliaW9eFKbdzd0U3GjbjVmMiarK2ncOxyhTDKiaGQLEG5e96f2vqIOzQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">该项目旨在通过个性化融合技术实现视觉语言推荐系统的联邦学习。</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">代码使用</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">Python</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">PyTorch</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">实现，支持</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">多模态数据集</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">的处理。项目适用于学术研究，用户可以在自己的风险下运行。</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">项目提供了论文“Federated Vision-Language-Recommendation with Personalized Fusion”的源代码。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/fedvlr\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/fedvlr</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③项目：Lumos-Custom</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"488\" data-imgfileid=\"100016903\" data-ratio=\"0.41944444444444445\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1164\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e5fbc87b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxVmPWFFeEkavAlbnNGrPn9QQFWqAcibCIbUOxsQB9Me77mqsn4uOGD2zCPjysdgzgcblOmGEZx5rg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Lumos-Custom项目是阿里巴巴达摩院的一个研究项目，专注于定制化视频生成。该项目提出了UniLumos，一个统一的重光照框架，旨在通过RGB空间几何反馈来增强图像和视频的物理一致性。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">UniLumos通过监督模型输出的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">深度</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">法线图</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，显式地将光照效果与场景结构对齐，从而提高物理合理性。项目还设计了一个</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">六维注释协议</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">和</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">LumosBench基准</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，用于评估光照可控性和精度。实验表明，UniLumos在图像和视频重光照方面实现了显著的物理一致性改进，并提高了计算效率。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/lumos-custom\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/lumos-custom</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">④项目：Autonomous Researcher</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"400\" data-imgfileid=\"100016902\" data-ratio=\"0.3425925925925926\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1166\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5c5e48fa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FGU2ibjU7TDkxVmPWFFeEkavAlbnNGrPn9CorDacXnbzfr5plkNuhm9z6Nk8F3DTTIXMcILWJ3ukRphCmSlsBibLw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Autonomous Researcher 是一个自主的人工智能研究工具。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">它能够接收研究目标，将其分解为多个实验，并为每个实验启动独立的Agent，这些Agent可以访问自己的GPU进行模型训练、推理等操作。最终，系统会将实验结果整理成论文风格的报告。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:4px;outline:0px;color:rgb(255, 104, 39);letter-spacing:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;text-align:start;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/autonomous-researcher-2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/autonomous-researcher-2</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文汇总了 2025 年 11 月 25 日的最新开源 AI 项目，包括微软的 Fara 多模态 SLM、量子增强推理模型 Hypnos-i1、阿里巴巴的定制化视频生成 Lumos-Custom 等。",
